de.mpg.biochem.mars.molecule

Interface MoleculeArchiveProperties<M extends Molecule,I extends MarsMetadata>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JsonConvertibleRecord
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMoleculeArchiveProperties, ArchMoleculeArchiveProperties, DefaultMoleculeArchiveProperties, DnaMoleculeArchiveProperties, SingleMoleculeArchiveProperties

    public interface MoleculeArchiveProperties<M extends Molecule,I extends MarsMetadata>
extends JsonConvertibleRecord
    Global properties of Molecule Archives are stored in MoleculeArchiveProperties including comments, number of each record type, as well as tag, parameter, Table column, region and position name indexes. Information you would like to know without having to read the entire archive record-by-record.
    Author:
    Karl Duderstadt
